## Sprint progress
- Sprint 1 (Foundation rebuild): COMPLETE
  - Refactored `src/cli.js` into modules under `src/`.
  - Added dependencies: `cheerio`, `openai`, `@anthropic-ai/sdk`.
  - Added provider-agnostic LLM config scaffold in `src/llm.js`; no network LLM calls yet.
  - Added structured proof-point fields: skills, metrics, source, metadata.
  - Expanded default profile preferences: role families, industries, stages, locations, salary, dealbreakers, work model, communication style, strategy, automation policy.
  - Added REST API scaffold with local CRUD-style routes for profiles, proofs, jobs, applications, tasks, artifacts, companies, stakeholders, plus `/api/state`.
  - Added local API write protections: rejects non-local `Origin` writes and reloads the sql.js DB before API requests to avoid stale server snapshots overwriting newer CLI changes.
  - README updated for modular architecture, dependencies, LLM scaffold, REST examples, and deterministic degraded-mode status.
  - Tests expanded from 2 to 3 subtests covering REST proof/task creation, CSRF/origin guard, stale-DB protection, and parsed API state.
- Sprint 2 (LLM scoring + tailoring): NOT STARTED — NEXT
